{
  "stem": "26983.10",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know, also, there was a time when we could choose to go on a transport, meaning that we have a choice-- as if a choice-- to go out of Auschwitz-- I mean, from the danger to be gassed.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the danger-- our danger was that we will be-- we will be dying in the work--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--out work and hard work, or by-- be killed off by the SS men and so on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, because I was so weak and small, choose-- I said, as long as I am here, well, maybe I will end in the gas chambers, but this is only suffering for a comparatively short time.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as long as I'm here, I know how to get enough food not to starve.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whereupon to go out, I didn't know what will happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Most probably.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, what I was, at that time, is very curious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just in puberty.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wanted to know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And something was pushing me-- I have to remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was drawing, also, in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had some papers from time to time with a pencil.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But of course, these drawings I had to hide or they were lost.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I reconstructed them at once after the war-- at once when I was able to walk and to draw.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After I got my typhoid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think it was in July '45, I made these drawings about the crematorium, et cetera, and the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I will show you afterwards.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before the march, I would like to mention something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even the block 13 was liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Evacuated.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came to a different block, number 29, which was a children block, a Jugend block.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
